# Page title auto-generated from resource name

Manages a file in the Komodor Klaudia Knowledge Base.

Knowledge Base files provide contextual runbook-style documentation that Klaudia AI uses when performing root cause analysis (RCA). Files can be optionally scoped to specific clusters.

> **Note:** Because the API does not support in-place file updates, any change to `filename`, `content`, or `clusters` will cause the resource to be destroyed and re-created.

